  # Dev Login
  
  Development-only login endpoint. Select a mock user by ID.
  
  ## Available Users
  - User 1: Alice Johnson (1,000,000 CLP)
  - User 2: Bob Smith (20,000 CLP)
  - User 3: Charlie Brown (100,000 CLP)
  
  ## Expected Response
  ```json
  {
    "user_id": 1,
    "name": "Alice Johnson",
    "balance_clp": 1000000.0
  }
  ```
}
